<div class="col s12 ">

  <% if session[:logged_in] == true %>
    <% @posts.each do |post| %>
        <div class="post">
          <p>This is <%= User[id: post.poster_id].username %> </p>
          <p><%= post.description %> </p>
          <p>TELL HER HOW GOOD SHE LOOKS!</p>
          <p>Likes:  <%= post.vote_amount %> </p>
          <br />

          <form action="/post/voteup" method="post">
            <div class="form-group">
              <input type="hidden" name="id" value="<%= post.id %>">
              <button class="btn-primary" type="submit" name="button">Vote up</button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
    <% end %>
  <% else %>
    <div class="welcome">
      <h1>Welcome to YOU LOOK GOOD!</h1>
      <p>Women regularly ask the question: "How do I look?" This is a site to tell you YOU LOOK GOOD! What you see isn't what the world sees. You may see imperfections. We see beauty. We see uniqueness. See the beauty that we see!!! Post pictures of yourself and get ready to feel the love from the YLG community! We are a culture of positivity - any negative comments will be removed! Please post responsibly. No nudity or graphic content!</p>
      <h3>Please sign in to get started!</h3>
      <img src="images/always_like_a_girl1.jpg" />
    </div>
    <div class="links">
          <div class="row container">
            <div class="col s12">
              <div class="">
                <h2 class="section-title">Feeling down? Let us lift you up!</h2>
                <p>Some of our favorite videos that reaffirm you look good, and man it feels good to be a woman!</p>
              </div>
              <div class="slider">
                   <ul class="slides hoverable">
                     <li>
                       <img class="carousel-image" src="images/always_like_a_girl1.jpg" /></a>
                       <div class="carousel-text">
                         <h3>#likeagirl</h3>
                         <h5>Does it ever get old? No. Do we cry every time? Yes. </h5>
                         <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XjJQBjWYDTs">WATCH HERE</a>
                       </div>
                     </li>
                     <li>
                       <img class="carousel-image" src="images/secret_commercial.jpg" />
                       <div class="carousel-text">
                         <h3>Bridge That Gap</h3>
                         <h5>A recent ad for Secret that pumps me up every time. Do it.</h5>
                         <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9ilSeJ6B5ro">WATCH HERE</a>
                       </div>
                     </li>
                     <li>
                       <img class="carousel-image" src="images/you_can_be_anything.jpg" />
                       <div class="carousel-text">
                         <h3>You Can Be Anything. Barbie</h3>
                         <h5>We were jazzed when Barbie expanded skin color, height and size. And now there's this. You're welcome.</h5>
                         <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l1vnsqbnAkk">WATCH HERE</a>
                       </div>
                     </li>
                   </ul>
                 </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div id="causes" class="slide" data-anchor="causes">
          <div class="row container">
            <div class="col s12">
              <h2 class="section-title">CAUSES I <span class="red-word">CARE</span> ABOUT</h2>
              <p>Clothing and computers take up most of my life. Here are some causes that add a lot more meaning to it. Check them out and feel free to donate or get involved with these amazing organizations!</p>
              <div class="slider">
                   <ul class="slides hoverable">
                     <li>
                       <a href="http://diabetesfoundation.jdrf.com/info/jdrf/"><img class="carousel-image" src="images/jdrf-walk.jpg"></a>
                       <div class="carousel-text">
                         <h3>Juvenile Diabetes Research Foundation</h3>
                         <h5>With a best friend and Grandma affected by Type 1 Diabetes, this is a cause near and dear to my heart.</h5>
                       </div>
                     </li>
                     <li>
                       <a href="http://www.aphasia.org/"><img class="carousel-image" src="images/rob-aphasia-pic.jpg"></a>
                       <div class="carousel-text">
                         <h3>National Aphasia Association</h3>
                         <h5>A coworker and friend had a stroke at work and now has lost most ability to speak. After learning so much from him, I want to help fight to make sure he and all those affected by Aphasia get back the vital ability of speech.</h5>
                       </div>
                     </li>
                     <li>
                       <a href="http://www.aidschicago.org/"><img class="carousel-image" src="images/aids-foundation-chicago.jpg"></a>
                       <div class="carousel-text">
                         <h3>AIDS Foundation of Chicago</h3>
                         <h5>Great events. Great cause. Check out ways to get involved.</h5>
                       </div>
                     </li>
                   </ul>
                 </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  <% end %>

</div>
